    <abstract>
      <t>&lt;p&gt;This document describes two TFTP options.  The first allows the client and server to negotiate the Timeout Interval.  The second allows the side receiving the file to determine the ultimate size of the transfer before it begins. [STANDARDS-TRACK]&lt;/p&gt;</t>
